      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 BrainDead Remove Background",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead \u2014 Remove Background\n\nSelf-contained background removal in one node. SAM3 text-grounded segmentation finds the subject, optional pymatting refines hair/edge transparency, then outputs RGBA + white/black composites.\n\n## Flow\n1. **LoadImage** \u2014 load any image.\n2. **BD Remove Background** \u2014 SAM3 segments by text prompt \u2192 hole fill \u2192 matting \u2192 crop \u2192 RGBA output.\n\n## Key Settings\n- **prompts** \u2014 one SAM3 prompt per line. Union-combined. Try: `person`, `character`, `product`, `animal`.\n- **negative_prompts** \u2014 punch out regions that bleed into the subject (e.g. `background`, `wall`).\n- **matting_mode: closed_form** \u2014 pymatting edge refinement. Best for hair and soft edges. Requires `pip install pymatting`.\n- **matting_mode: none** \u2014 hard mask from SAM3 only. Fastest.\n- **mask_mode** (with external_mask input):\n  - `constrain` \u2014 intersect SAM3 with your mask (rough silhouette clamp)\n  - `subtract` \u2014 cut an already-masked region out of SAM3 result\n  - `use_directly` \u2014 skip SAM3, apply hole-fill + matting to your mask only\n- **crop_to_content** \u2014 trims the canvas to the subject bounding box + padding.\n- **output_size** \u2014 set to 512 or 1024 with `pad_square` to get a fixed-size output.\n\n## Outputs\n- **rgba** \u2014 4-channel RGBA (plug into BD_PackChannels or 3D pipelines)\n- **mask** \u2014 alpha mask only (wire to BD_MaskBatchIndex, BD_FillMaskHoles, etc.)\n- **rgb_white_bg** \u2014 composited over white (good for 3D UV bake preview)\n- **rgb_black_bg** \u2014 composited over black\n- **crop_box** \u2014 `x0,y0,x1,y1` of the crop in the original image coordinates\n\n## Models (auto-load)\n- SAM3 + CLIP: loaded from `/srv/AI_Stuff/models/sam/` on first run.\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)\n"
      ]
    },
